    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Practice and perfect your ninja skills with the ASR Tactical 6pc Kunai Throwing Knife Set!</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Tactical 6 Inch Drop Point Ninja Kunai Throwing Knives Set (2 Set Sizes)</h2>\n  <p>Practice and perfect your ninja skills with the ASR Tactical 6pc Kunai Throwing Knife Set!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>BALANCED FOR ACCURATE THROWING - Each 6-inch kunai is carefully balanced with a centered point of gravity to promote smooth, consistent rotation and improved throwing accuracy during practice.</li>\n    <li>DURABLE 440 STAINLESS STEEL CONSTRUCTION - Made from a single solid piece of 440 stainless steel from tip to handle, providing strength, corrosion resistance, and long-lasting durability through repeated training sessions.</li>\n    <li>VERSATILE CORD-WRAPPED GRIP - The single-edge design with cord-wrapped handles allows multiple grip options, letting you throw from either the handle or blade side for a variety of throwing styles and techniques.</li>\n    <li>REINFORCED NYLON CARRY SHEATH - Includes a durable nylon sheath with individual compartments to keep each knife separated, helping prevent dulling and protecting the finish. Built-in belt loop allows for easy transport.</li>\n    <li>MULTIPLE SET OPTIONS - Available in 3-piece or 6-piece sets, giving beginners and experienced throwers the flexibility to choose the quantity that best suits their training setup.</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/73506/jAm3ecBQ6UvpqwPwAxUvDKeZHfNi6M-metaNnBjX25pbmphX2tuaXZlcy5qcGc=-.jpg\" alt=\"Practice and perfect your ninja skills with the ASR Tactical 6pc Kunai Throwing Knife Set\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <p>Carefully balanced with the center of gravity in the middle of the knives, these blades will make even, round circles in flight. The single-edged cord-wrapped blades will give you the option to grip them from either the handle or the blade side, and allow for more variation in throwing techniques.</p>\n  <p>The 440 stainless steel construction will keep these knives in great condition through many practice sessions. The solid piece of steel from tip to handle ensures you won&#039;t have to worry about losing rivets or parts of the handle if you accidentally hit a rock.</p>\n  <p>Included is a reinforced nylon sheath that will hold all three knives. The sheath even includes a belt loop for easy transportation. Each knife has its own compartment, so you&#039;ll be able to keep them separate to resist dulling and help maintain the amazing finish.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
